Guitar Center is an American musical instrument retailer chain based in Westlake Village, California. It is the largest company of its kind in the United States, with 304 locations. The company oversees subsidiaries which include Musician\'s Friend, AVDG, Music & Arts, Woodwind & Brasswind, and Giardinelli.
